description:
As a job seeker
  I want to apply for jobs
  So that I can have a chance to get a job
name: Apply with Resume

elements.name: Existing member with resume can start apply

steps.name: I type in email of account with resume on email field
I type in password of account with resume on password field
I should see Logged In Header module
I should land on Search Result page
I go to the 2nd Job Ad
I should land on Job Ad page
I should land on Apply page

description:
As a job seeker
  I want to apply for jobs
  So that I can have a chance to get a job
name: Apply without Resume

elements.name: Existing member without resume cannot start apply

steps.name: I type in email of account without resume on email field
I type in password of account without resume on password field
I should see Logged In Header module
I should land on Search Result page
I go to the 1st Job Ad
I should land on Job Ad page
I should land on Complete Your Profile page
I should see App Store button

description:
As a job seeker
  I want to login
  So that I can use the features for logged in members
name: Login

elements.name: Existing member cannot login with incorrect email & password

steps.name: I type in carrielai@seekasia.com on email field
I type in WrongPassword on password field
error alert pops up: Either the user name or password was entered incorrectly, please try again.

elements.name: User can go to create an account from Login page

steps.name: I should land on Sign Up page

elements.name: User can go to Forgot password page from Login page

steps.name: I should land on Forgot Password page

description:
As a job seeker
  I want to search for jobs
  So that I can see new posted jobs
name: Search

steps.name: I should land on Search Result page
the Search criteria contains all jobs
I type in QA Analyst on Keyword field
I should land on Search Result page
the Search criteria contains QA Analyst

elements.name: Search by job function ( level one job function )

steps.name: I select Accounting from Job function list
I should land on Search Result page

elements.name: Search by job function ( level two job function )

steps.name: I select Accountant from Job function list
I should land on Search Result page

elements.name: Change salary from monthly to hourly
